          "date": "2026-04-15 18:38:15.000000000",
          "tz": 0
        },
        "subject": "LU-12668 tests: add EC failure orchestrator",
        "message": "LU-12668 tests: add EC failure orchestrator\n\n--WIP--\n\nThis is an early version of an automated stresstest / failure\ninjection / benchmarking tool for EC. It can currently only be run\nby the user, but will be adapted to allow integration to sanity-ec.\n\nAt its current state the user can disabled specific OSTs, see\nwhich OSTs contain the parity information, run a basic read on a\ncreated file and see the results. 8 OSTs are required to run for\nnow.\n\nAdded different layout options and added action logging for\nbug recreation.\n\nGoing to rebase ontop 64938 to see how things go.\n\nTest-Parameters: forbuildonly\nSigned-off-by: Maximilian Dilger <mdilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ic53df83e733c8850a9435b6793e4be431156b24a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master",
      "description": "Rebase"
    }
